Privacy policy
This privacy policy explains to you the type, scope and purpose of the processing of personal data (hereinafter referred to as "data") within our online service and the associated websites, functions and contents as well as external online presences, e.g. our social media profile. (hereinafter jointly referred to as "online service"). With regard to the terms used, such as "processing", "responsible for the content" or "person in charge", we refer to the definitions in Art. 4 of the Datenschutzgrundverordnung (DSGVO).
Responsible for the content
Wavedash GmbH
Mühlenstr. 8a
14167 Berlin
Germany
Emailaddress: hello@rocket-league.com
Legal information:
https://rocket-league.com/legal
